      h6.light We have benefitted a lot from open source
      h6.light So to return the favor, we open source all non critical code
      h6.light
        'Don't forget to check us out on
        a href="https://github.com/organizations/thoughtnirvana" Github

      .row
        - repos.each do |repo|
          .col.s12.m4.l4
            .repo.card.amber.lighten-5.hoverable
              .card-content
                a.teal-text href=repo["link"] = repo["header"]
                p.light = repo["description"]
              .card-action
                span.card-title = repo["language"]

